spec_data.Name: perl-Devel-Trace
spec_data.Description:
If you run your program with perl -d:Trace program, this module will print
a message to standard error just before each line is executed.

This is something like the shell's -x option.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 11:05:01 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Print out each line before it is executed (like sh -x)
